  • Method Details

    • findApprenticeAcademicYearNotArchivedByYear

      @Query("SELECT ay FROM AcademicYear ay LEFT JOIN ay.apprentice a LEFT JOIN ay.year y WHERE a.archived = FALSE AND y.id = :yearId") List<AcademicYear> findApprenticeAcademicYearNotArchivedByYear(@Param("yearId") UUID yearId)
      Retrieves all non-archived academic years for apprentices associated with a specific academic year.
      Parameters:
      yearId - the unique identifier of the academic year
      Returns:
      a list of active (non-archived) apprentice academic year records

    • findAcademicYearByApprenticeAndYear

      @Query("SELECT DISTINCT ay.id FROM AcademicYear ay LEFT JOIN ay.apprentice a LEFT JOIN ay.year y WHERE a.id = :apprenticeId AND y.id = :yearId") List<UUID> findAcademicYearByApprenticeAndYear(@Param("apprenticeId") UUID apprenticeId, @Param("yearId") UUID yearId)
      Retrieves the list of academic year IDs associated with a specific apprentice and academic year.
      Parameters:
      apprenticeId - the unique identifier of the apprentice
      yearId - the unique identifier of the academic year
      Returns:
      a list of matching academic year IDs

    • getApprenticeAcademicYearInfoByYearAndTutor

      @Query("SELECT ay FROM AcademicYear ay LEFT JOIN ay.apprentice a LEFT JOIN ay.year y LEFT JOIN ay.company c LEFT JOIN ay.missions m LEFT JOIN ay.mentor me WHERE a.tutor.id = :tutorId AND NOT (ay.studyLevel = :studyLevel AND a.archived IS TRUE)AND y.id = :yearId") List<AcademicYear> getApprenticeAcademicYearInfoByYearAndTutor(@Param("tutorId") UUID tutorId, @Param("studyLevel") StudyLevel studyLevel, @Param("yearId") UUID yearId)
      Retrieves academic year records for apprentices supervised by a specific tutor and linked to a given academic year, excluding archived apprentices matching the specified study level.
      Parameters:
      tutorId - the unique identifier of the tutor
      studyLevel - the study level used to filter out archived apprentices
      yearId - the unique identifier of the academic year
      Returns:
      a list of academic year records matching the tutor and year criteria

    • researchApprentices

      @Query("SELECT ay FROM AcademicYear ay LEFT JOIN ay.apprentice a LEFT JOIN ay.year y LEFT JOIN ay.company c LEFT JOIN ay.missions m LEFT JOIN ay.mentor me WHERE a.lastName LIKE concat('%', :apprenticeName, '%') AND c.name LIKE concat('%', :companyName, '%') AND (:year <= 0 OR FUNCTION('YEAR', y.year) = :year) AND (( :missionKeywords = '' OR EXISTS (SELECT ay1.id FROM AcademicYear ay1 LEFT JOIN ay1.missions m1 WHERE ay1.id = ay.id AND m1.keywords LIKE concat('%', :missionKeywords, '%')))) ORDER BY y.year ") List<AcademicYear> researchApprentices(@Param("apprenticeName") String apprenticeName, @Param("companyName") String companyName, @Param("missionKeywords") String missionKeywords, @Param("year") int academicYear)
      Searches for academic year records of apprentices based on multiple optional criteria, including apprentice name, company name, mission keywords, and academic year.
      Parameters:
      apprenticeName - partial or full apprentice last name to filter by
      companyName - partial or full company name to filter by
      missionKeywords - keywords to match within missions
      academicYear - the academic year to filter by; ignored if is less or equal to 0
      Returns:
      a list of academic year records matching the specified search criteria, ordered by year
